This prefab is only used in Trikz maps. Its a pretty hard Trikz challenge. You have to boost your parter two times in a row, to get to the next level. Good for trikzters that are looking for a bigger challenge.

Use it as much as you want.
Credits is required if you are gonna use this prefab, but you think that this is a problem, please contact me, and we may find another solution.

Thank you.
